relation: Steer clear. Just steer clear of him.
Owner of Jackie's Cafe, where the walls are not alive. I don't care what you've heard.

My interpretation of the janitor from M1. He may sometimes say mean things about her, but deep down, he loves his wife dearly. Oh, and he also knows when a clock is twenty minutes fast, so, be sure to adjust your watches.
Poor Jeff. There is a well-known theory that if an Elder Mook is glaring at you with its eerie eyes, look away and you'll be fine. Of course, there is no scienitific evidence to support this theory.
Now he can figure out the length (and width) of things easily!
